386
00:16:20,849 --> 00:16:23,025
Mustard? Also a condiment.

387
00:16:23,069 --> 00:16:24,984
Hummus is like a side dish.

388
00:16:25,027 --> 00:16:26,768
No, no. Hummus is a dip.

389
00:16:26,811 --> 00:16:29,118
Easy, condiment king.

390
00:16:29,162 --> 00:16:31,077
I don't need you
Runksplaining hummus to me!

391
00:16:31,120 --> 00:16:32,339
Well, I don't need you being

392
00:16:32,382 --> 00:16:33,731
so cavalier
with our sandwiches.

393
00:16:33,775 --> 00:16:35,646
Well, don't worry,
because I am never

394
00:16:35,690 --> 00:16:37,822
bringing you lunch ever again.
- [scoffs]

395
00:16:37,866 --> 00:16:39,824
- Ugh!
- Sorry, sorry.

396
00:16:39,868 --> 00:16:42,436
Do you guys know
where the arctic parkas are?

397
00:16:42,479 --> 00:16:45,221
- The cozy ones?
- Yeah.

398
00:16:45,265 --> 00:16:47,745
- Starchives.
- Right.

399
00:16:47,789 --> 00:16:50,009
Thank you. Gotta run.

400
00:16:50,052 --> 00:16:51,314
[scoffs]

401
00:16:51,358 --> 00:16:53,795
[notification chimes,
phone buzzes]

402
00:16:54,883 --> 00:16:55,840
<i>[tense music]</i>

403
00:16:55,884 --> 00:16:57,842
CCC tip app's blowing up.

404
00:16:57,886 --> 00:17:00,628
Something crazy is happening
at O'Shaughnessy's.

405
00:17:00,671 --> 00:17:02,847
Is Blockbuster here
to settle his late fees?

406
00:17:02,891 --> 00:17:05,241
No, it's not Blockbuster.

407
00:17:05,285 --> 00:17:07,243
But I have a feeling
we're gonna wish it was.

408
00:17:07,287 --> 00:17:08,636
<i>[dance music playing]</i>

409
00:17:08,679 --> 00:17:11,552
[glass shattering]
- Oh, come on, man!

410
00:17:11,595 --> 00:17:12,335
<i>♪</i>

411
00:17:12,379 --> 00:17:13,554
<i>[record scratches]</i>

412
00:17:13,597 --> 00:17:14,642
[music stops]

413
00:17:16,165 --> 00:17:18,341
<i>[The Death Set's</i> <i>
"Bad Decisions"]</i>

414
00:17:18,385 --> 00:17:20,865
I am a party god!

415
00:17:20,909 --> 00:17:24,695
<i>♪ I like making</i> <i>
bad decisions ♪</i>

416
00:17:24,739 --> 00:17:29,483
<i>♪ Is this ever gonna change?</i>

417
00:17:29,526 --> 00:17:31,224
[bottle shatters]
[growling]

418
00:17:31,267 --> 00:17:33,530
We can never unsee this.

419
