00:18:31,284 --> 00:18:33,764
<i>[tense music]</i>

444
00:18:33,808 --> 00:18:35,462
[glass shattering]

445
00:18:35,505 --> 00:18:36,811
[thud]

446
00:18:36,854 --> 00:18:37,812
[grunts]

447
00:18:37,855 --> 00:18:39,509
<i>[quirky music]</i>

448
00:18:39,553 --> 00:18:42,730
[panting]

449
00:18:42,773 --> 00:18:44,340
Oh, a big night out, huh?

450
00:18:44,384 --> 00:18:46,734
Yeah, I've been there myself.

451
00:18:46,777 --> 00:18:49,911
Now, sure, right now,
love is all cupcakes,

452
00:18:49,954 --> 00:18:51,565
puppies, and monster trucks.

453
00:18:51,608 --> 00:18:53,828
But just you wait
until one of you dies

454
00:18:53,871 --> 00:18:57,092
battling an interdimensional
death demon.

455
00:18:57,136 --> 00:18:58,789
Oh, yeah.

456
00:18:58,833 --> 00:19:00,269
